                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Dawson</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Para phrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Santo Domingo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1904-11-28">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 28, 1904</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Dawson reports that under certain contingencies the President of the
                    Dominican Republic will renew the request that the financial agent take charge
                    of the four ports.)</p>
            </div>
